{"tid":507591,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"又到聖誕,仲唔揀返粒PANDORA畀女友?","createTime":"2017-12-23T12:05:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-23T13:49:10.000Z","uid":25125,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"93a692b60f4d76e420bf20b1fd0dec7ccb4c6ebb","tid":507591,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T12:05:19.000Z","msg":"話說今日我搭返上次聽到兩條死港女講好閪想有男人送PANDORA比佢果條扶手梯既時候 <br />\n竟然比我見到呢間咁既垃圾豬二醒PANDORA呀 <br />\n裡面充斥住一個二個, 唔係港女唔係肥師奶 <br />\n係一個二個牛高馬大既男人呀 <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/n2DlaaN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fn2DlaaN.jpg&h=93c660e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌你真係唔撚係有相我諗你地都唔會信 <br />\n男人之家, 就算未撚睇過我寫果篇文, 未撚比人屌過你買PANDORA係幾咁ON9既一件事呀 <br />\n你都唔會咁拿柒, 成班麻甩佬走入去呢間野度呀? <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/dOMhSlv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FdOMhSlv.jpg&h=5a381209&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喂喂喂, 做乜撚野事呀你地而家 <br />\n惠康聖誕大特賣啊? <br />\n十幾廿碌棍走入去呢間女人野豬二醒度迫, 排撚哂長龍咁 <br />\n喂大佬, 玻璃窗黎架, 出面睇到哂你地架, 貪好睇咩屌 <br />\n<br />\n即係唔係唔撚畀你地買首飾LUM女呀 <br />\n屌你都識揀呀下話? 要貴既有周XX, 平少少既有XXBELLE <br />\n再唔係你CHEAP少少啊, 走入去LOG-ON都起碼叫有粒天然水晶鑲係戒指度, 而且二百零蚊有膠液 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>屌你班傻鳩港男, 擘撚大你地對眼, 睇清楚你洗左四百蚊買一粒乜春啦!</strong> </span><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/qx0w9zr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fqx0w9zr.jpg&h=d89dbad0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/snzXDTL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FsnzXDTL.jpg&h=3be235ac&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嘩屌你老母, 琉璃啊, 好撚浪漫啊個名 <br />\n屌你冇撚讀過書都應該知, 琉璃即係玻璃呀傻鳩 <br />\n英文係GLASS呀! (利申英文有E <br />\n屌你再睇下$699果D又有乜? <br />\nCubic zirconia 簡稱CZ, 即係人造石, 一百蚊有幾卡果D呀傻仔! <br />\n以呢D咁細粒既黎計, 一百蚊分分鐘有50粒添呀傻仔! <br />\n<br />\n傻仔! <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">傻仔!</span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">傻仔! </span><br />\n<br />\n屌你班懵撚真係影衰哂有鳩既動物 <br />\n我知實有人話原材料價值唔可以代表貨物價錢架啦 <br />\n喂屌你咩.............. <br />\n咁你睇下佢標個價幾撚ON9先得架 <br />\n再唔該你搭MTR去九龍塘站, 行果條隧道去又一城 <br />\n睇下你班懵撚水魚, 貼撚左幾撚多錢比呢間咁既豬二醒PANDORA <br />\n包起差唔多成條隧道黎賣廣告啦 <br />\n<br />\n傻仔! <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">傻仔!</span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">傻仔! </span><br />\n<br />\n嘩我屌, 我真係真心想代呢間ON9公司多謝你班買垃圾都仲要排住隊去, 執輸行頭既ON9港男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原文: <a href=\"http://archive.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5576450&amp;sensormode=N\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Farchive.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D5576450%26sensormode%3DN&d=pg4RXjSvMZlgN6Im%2F0x5HIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=66849de8\" target=\"_blank\">http://archive.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5576450&amp;sensormode=N</a>"},{"pid":"d3394aa309c238e4e2d5bf4b988d9123fe3e672f","tid":507591,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T12:16:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"136e9127b56b6a23419afa50635279e4276129db","tid":507591,"uid":33886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T12:20:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9944ce1e2f11500df809c9b287d8bf269041d3af","tid":507591,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T12:27:56.000Z","msg":"最後咪又係買<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d4990703a269c60fdbe7a7c30780f3e573b4c5","tid":507591,"uid":10079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T13:22:25.000Z","msg":"買呢啲不如求鳩其買ysl<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa223ac181a281f7bf64e8229ab294f3a0b8b7ce","tid":507591,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T13:34:03.000Z","msg":"又回帶?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"